---
---
  <section id="experience" class="space-y-4 mb-16 font-mono text-[13px]" aria-label="Experience History">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-6">
      <span class="text-green-500 font-bold opacity-80">~</span>
      <span class="text-muted-foreground/50">$</span>
      <span class="text-foreground">cat history.log</span>
    </div>

    <div class="pl-0 sm:pl-6 space-y-10">
      {/* Experience 1 */}
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="text-foreground font-medium flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-between gap-1">
          <span>[2025-Present] Lead Frontend Developer @ Hospio360</span>
          <span class="text-muted-foreground/50">Remote</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Leading all frontend architecture for a pre-launch hotel management SaaS. Own the entire frontend across two surfaces — a Next.js marketing site and a TanStack Start operations dashboard.
        </p>
        <div class="text-muted-foreground opacity-80 pl-4 border-l border-border/40 space-y-2 pt-2">
          <div>> Architected the full frontend from scratch</div>
          <div>> Established component system and design tokens</div>
          <div>> Optimized performance and responsiveness</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Experience 2 */}
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="text-foreground font-medium flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-between gap-1">
          <span>[2023-2025] Fullstack Developer @ Wittyr</span>
          <span class="text-muted-foreground/50">Remote</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Built the core MVP using Next.js, tRPC, and Prisma. Implemented real-time collaboration features with WebSockets and designed a modular backend architecture to support scaling.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
